# JMCFI Clinic — Project Structure

## Stack

Django 5.2 · Channels 4.3 · django-allauth (Google OAuth) · HTMX 1.9 · Alpine.js 3.x · Tailwind CSS (CDN) · Font Awesome 6.4 · WhiteNoise · pdfkit · python-docx · `uv` package manager · SQLite (dev) / PostgreSQL (prod)

## App Map

| App | URL Prefix | Purpose |
|-----|-----------|---------|
| `core/` | `/` | Dashboard, auth, profiles, notifications, user management, search |
| `appointments/` | `/appointments/` | Scheduling & management |
| `medical_records/` | `/medical-records/` | Medical records CRUD |
| `dental_records/` | `/dental-records/` | Dental records + charting |
| `document_request/` | `/documents/` | Certificate/document requests + PDF generation |
| `feedback/` | `/feedback/` | Feedback submission & stats |
| `health_tips/` | `/health-tips/` | Health tips/articles with markdown |
| `health_forms_services/` | `/health-forms/` | Health forms, dental forms, prescriptions, patient charts |
| `analytics/` | `/analytics/` | Cross-app analytics & reporting |
| `pharmacy/` | `/pharmacy/` | Inventory, dispensing, purchase orders |
| `messaging/` | `/messages/` | Direct messages & announcements |

## Roles

`admin` · `doctor` · `staff` · `student` — defined in `core/models.py User.ROLE`

## File Navigation

| Need to... | Look in |
|---|---|
| Find all URL routes | `backend/urls.py` → each app's `urls.py` |
| Add a view | App's `views.py` (or `views/` package for `health_forms_services`) |
| Add a model | App's `models.py` |
| Add a form | App's `forms.py` |
| Add a template | App's `templates/<app_name>/` |
| Change auth logic | `core/adapters.py`, `core/signals.py` |
| Change middleware | `core/middleware.py` |
| Change profile policy | `core/profile_policy.py` |
| HTMX utilities | `core/htmx_utils.py` |
| Role decorators | `core/decorators.py` |
| Context processors | `core/context_processors.py` |
| Add dependencies | `pyproject.toml` (never requirements.txt) |

## Template Locations

- `core/templates/core/base.html` — base layout with sidebar, nav, scripts
- `core/templates/core/partials/` — staff/student profile field partials
- `core/templates/core/user_management/` — user CRUD, audit, cleanup
- `templates/partials/` — shared form error fragments
- `templates/components/` — shared `modal.html`
- `health_forms_services/` — `_new` suffixed variants for CBV templates, `_base_*.html` base templates

## Key Architecture

- **Auth**: Google OAuth only, no passwords. `NoPasswordAdapter` + `GoogleOnlyAdapter` in `core/adapters.py`
- **Profiles**: `StudentProfile` / `StaffProfile` with completion enforcement via `ProfileCompleteMiddleware`
- **Middleware chain**: `UserActivityMiddleware` → `SessionTimeoutMiddleware` → `RoleMiddleware` → `ProfileCompleteMiddleware`
- **Frontend**: HTMX for server communication, Alpine.js for local state, Tailwind CDN for styling
